::KitKat::

She ran from the base.  She had tried to do things and help her group 
and all she did was keep banging here head against walls.  She ran 
through the forest and ran towards Phobia's ship.  She opened her 
link.  "HEY Phobia, I'm heading towards your position.  I need your 
help."

She put on an extra burst of speed and ran with all her might towards 
Phobia's ship.
